        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "> you upgrade eslint version then you got it not work. so what's the problem of this plugin ?\n\nThe plugin should be upgraded to be compatible with the latest eslint version. Otherwise no one can use it with the latest eslint version, so no one will use it anymore. You can't prevent people from upgrading eslint version.\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c55c1684-e6f7-4071-afff-6a38d7810f13)\nthe `eslint.experimental.useFlatConfig` option is deprecated and won't work for eslint 9, so it should be updated to `eslint.useFlatConfig` if flat config files are detected\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/3184 This shouldn't have been reverted, just adding the deprecated experiment key back\n",
